1. ACTION: user react to post 

if (user didn't react yet to post)
  2. FRONT : increase reaction counter
  3. FRONT : select reaction icon
  4. BACK : upload new reaction   OK

else if (user already react with an other reaction)
  2. FRONT : decrease previous reaction counter
  3. FRONT : unselect previous reaction icon
  if (new_reaction != last_reaction)
    4. FRONT : update new reaction
    5. BACK : update reaction
  else
    4. BACK : DELETE previous reaction


